description: Yes there are some late 60s and early 80s songs (and one from the 50s some may argue the 00s, but it's worth it cause it's a good song) but IT'S FINE they balance each other out and average to 70s kinda sorta. Also I'd like to acknoweldge how painful Margaritaville is but I feel like it has to stay
